Record Class Some<T>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.github.jorgericovivas.rust_essentials.option.Some<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the value.
Record Components:
value - the existing value.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Option<T>
public record Some<T>(T value) extends Record implements Option<T>
Represents an existing and non-null value.

Example: In searching an index of a List whose element matches a Predicate, the resulting value could be Option<Integer>, and when present, the operation would return a Some<Integer> containing the index of the value matching this predicate.
